    "reviewer_summary": "The agent correctly identified the need to find Tesla's earnings date (call 1) and then search for news, but it fell into a recovery trap: it retried search_documents three times with minor parameter tweaks, all returning empty, and never attempted the more appropriate get_entity_news tool. The chain is logically ordered but inefficient due to redundant search calls and poor recovery. The single most impactful change would be to try get_entity_news after search_documents fails, as it is purpose-built for entity news retrieval and may have different data coverage.",
